query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('activemq',
'codeigniter-2',
'coffeescript',
'firebase',
'inheritance',
'nlp',
'requirejs',
'scheduled-tasks',
'substring',
'trigonometry',
'uigesturerecognizer',
'unity5',
'wpf-controls');
